{"tid":1810314,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"白宮網站有條奇怪既香港普選連署，不要亂簽。","createTime":"2020-01-03T18:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T07:09:48.000Z","uid":62011,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"59af49e402068675b6ed156d838dc9e4bd565c78","tid":1810314,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:26:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan?fbclid=IwAR3YAkhZ5Q12erKNpXLnRo56OWmqIuqMreo61Xe_KnbWOf8dsUbSw_HnO1k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3YAkhZ5Q12erKNpXLnRo56OWmqIuqMreo61Xe_KnbWOf8dsUbSw_HnO1k&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=a652f25a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan?fbclid=IwAR3YAkhZ5Q12erKNpXLnRo56OWmqIuqMreo61Xe_KnbWOf8dsUbSw_HnO1k</a><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Universal Suffrage Plan<br />\n認住發起人: Created by <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">C.C.</span></strong> on January 02, 2020<br />\n<br />\n內容:<br />\nAccording to the requirement of HKHRDA of 2019 , Hong Kong people now propose this as the plan of Hong Kong Universal Suffrage in 2020.<br />\n1. Amend District Council to House,Legislative Council to Senate.<br />\n(將香港區議會、立法會分別修改做眾議院、同參議院)<br />\n2. Senate members need to suggested by House and elected by valid voters.<br />\n(參議院成員需要由眾議院建議及合資格選民選出)<br />\n3. Amend Chief Executive to Prime Minister.<br />\n(將行政長官改名做總理)<br />\n4. Prime Minister should be elected by valid voters.<br />\n(總理需要合資格選民選出)<br />\n5. Cancel the age and nationality limitation of the Prime Minister.<br />\n(取消總理年齡限制同國籍限制)<br />\n6. Amend the pledge of loyalty to Hong Kong people instead of PROC.<br />\n(承諾效忠香港人)<br />\n7. Cancel NPC's power of the explanation and amendment of Basic Law , own by Hong Kong people instead.<br />\n(取消人大對基本法解釋的權利)<br />\n8. Repeal the political ability and influences of LOCPG and NPC.<br />\n(廢除LOCPG同人大政治影響力)<br />\n9. Power of citizens' initiative and law amendment power should be guaranteed.<br />\n(保證市民立法主動權及法律修改權力)<br />\n10. Impeach of PM of 60% in Congress(Both)<br />\n(議會需要60%先可以彈劾特首)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">先唔講點無取消功能組別??? 一人一票直選?</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n1-4 改左名等於普選左????<br />\n<br />\n5 取消總理年齡限制同國籍限制<br />\n//根據《香港特別行政區基本法》第44條，香港特別行政區行政長官必須符合以下所有條件：<br />\n年滿四十周歲<br />\n在香港通常居住連續滿二十年<br />\n在外國無居留權<br />\n是香港特別行政區永久性居民中的中國公民//<br />\n即係唔洗理會上面條件???  搵個住係香港超過20年既大陸官做都得??<br />\n<br />\n7-8 好似干預緊支那內政(唔太識法律)<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得呢個普選計劃好奇怪，不宜簽。"},{"pid":"de6f20183358ebe3794d8e2d134bbeae8b6de9c7","tid":1810314,"uid":6347,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:29:26.000Z","msg":"我有幫手推<br />\n沖涼果陣諗諗下都覺得怪怪地<br />\nUm....咁應該點好"},{"pid":"0c9a9f2c5bf0eb433f74398aef1462754d7e7cfd","tid":1810314,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"請冷處理"},{"pid":"5f5bc47f064d2b81765084b97ac1f61c4e93ec2d","tid":1810314,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"de6f20183358ebe3794d8e2d134bbeae8b6de9c7","tid":1810314,"uid":6347,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:29:26.000Z","msg":"我有幫手推<br />\n沖涼果陣諗諗下都覺得怪怪地<br />\nUm....咁應該點好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:31:28.000Z","msg":"冷處理"},{"pid":"225bef34ab08b481991a4836c9970b3d747bfca2","tid":1810314,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:31:49.000Z","msg":"但係5之前係一人一票？<br />\n<br />\n如果要搵大陸人做，咁合資格選民嘅定義係咩？"},{"pid":"4da16840074a770e61b9a191686d39658924809c","tid":1810314,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18:32:07.000Z","msg":"咁係咪應該搵人寫點樣普選？"},{"pid":"23df3b80a151a3dd7f6dac74f6e8d7ff2b41821d","tid":1810314,"uid":149161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T18: